==English==
===Noun===
'''spod'''
{{wikipedia}}
#(jargon) one who uses [[talker]]s
#(colloquial) one who excessively studies, similar to a [[swot]], but in addition is disliked by fellow students because of it.
====See also====
[[w:Talker|Wikipedia article on Talkers]]

===Verb===
'''to spod'''
#(jargon) the action of sitting at a computer on the internet, and wasting time (by reading [[webcomic]]s, using [[internet forum]]s, or reading random pages on [[Wikipedia]], for example).